{"id":250557,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/09/杨支柱-陈京华而不实（作者授权发布）/","date":"2012-09-07T05:00:19Z","modified":"2012-09-07T05:00:19Z","title":"杨支柱 | 陈京:华而不实（作者授权发布）","content":"<div>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>                            </span><span>                   </span></span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>                                               </span><span>   </span></span> <span>陈京</span></p>\n<p><span>华是开花的意思</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>实是结果的意思</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>华而不实</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>就是光开花</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>不结果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>说一个人华而不实</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>他会很不高兴</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>但我们会花很多钱买房买车</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>却不愿生孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这是不是一种华而不实的生活</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>政府拼命追求</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">GDP,</span> <span>却限制生孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>这是不是一种华而不实的政策</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p>\n<p><span>几乎所有国家的政府都鼓励生育</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>为什么中国政府限制生育</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>有人说中国人口太多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>其实日本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>英国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>德国</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>新加坡和很多别的国家的人口密度比中国高很多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>很多人照样想移民到那些地方</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>上海的人口密度比别的地方高很多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>我们都拼命想得到北京</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>上海的户口</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">. <span> </span></span><span>叫一个住在北京市的宣传计划生育的官员搬到人烟稀少的农村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>他愿意去吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>既然很多国家的人口密度比中国高</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>为何大家都觉得中国拥挤呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>这是由于中国几乎所有的权力和财富都集中在大城市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>人们想过好日子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>只能到这些城市</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">. <span> </span></span><span>所谓的人口问题其实是社会财富分配问题</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\n<p><span>有人说人口太多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>消耗太多资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>假设有两家人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>一家有四个小孩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>太太在家带孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>先生年薪十万</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>另一家没有一个小孩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>夫妻全力工作</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>每人年薪二十万</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>这两家人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>谁</span> <span>消耗更多资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>第一家人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>只有十万块钱收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>只能消耗十万块钱的资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>第二家人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>有四十万块钱收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>就会消耗四十万块钱的资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>消耗资源的能力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>取决于生活水平的高低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>如果真的担心消耗太多资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>就应该设法降低我们的生活水平</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这大概是绝大多数人所不愿意听到的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>有人说应该把中国人口数量控制在最佳水平</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>其实在生态学理论里</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>并没有最佳人口这个概念</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>你把某些人口减少了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>另外一些人口就会增加</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>来享用现有的资源</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>当中国政府企图减少中国人口时</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>世界人口正快速增长</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>有的人说小孩太多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>孩子质量会下降</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>这种说法有根据吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>越来越多的人到是看到独生子女的问题</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>一个子女少的社会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>社会凝聚力也低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>北约这么多国家</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这么先进的武器</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这么多钱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>为什么征服不了一个小小的阿富汗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>因为北约大部分国家出生率低</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>当兵的为谁卖命呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>而阿富汗的平均出生率是六</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>也就是说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>一个人是为六个兄弟姐妹而战</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>为六十个堂兄弟姐妹</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>表兄弟姐妹而战</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>也有人说多养孩子太累</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>有一个朋友</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>本来只有一个孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>整天说养孩子太累了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>我们告诉她</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>再生一个就不累了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>后来她终于又生了一个</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>现在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>她和她老公带着小儿子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>整天笑眯眯的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>再也没有听到他们说累了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>过来人都明白</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>只有一个小孩</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>心里最紧张</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>最累</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>孩子多了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>家长就轻松了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>有的人说现代社会</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>人口数量已经不重要了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>今年美国总统选举</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>共和党竞选者中</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>有两个是摩门教徒</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>罗姆尼和</span> <span>洪博培</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>一百多年前</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>摩门教只是一个小小的异端教派</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>但是摩门教鼓励生育</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>今天他们的政治力量就显然易见了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>一句老话</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>血浓于水</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n<p><span>我们再从经济学的角度探讨一胎政策</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>经济学里有一个叫做规模经营的理论</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>因为投资需要成本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>产出高回报才高</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>比如说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>一个人读了小学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>中学</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>本科</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>硕士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>博士</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>然后规定他一辈子只能写一篇文章</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这种规定合理吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span><span>为了生孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>两个人需要长到二十多岁或者三十多岁</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>组建一个一个家庭</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>需要多年的磨合</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>十月怀胎</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>经历生产之痛</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>养育之苦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>为第一个孩子的来临投入了大量的成本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>积累了宝贵的经验</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>可是在一胎化政策下</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>这些宝贵的经验就白白的浪费掉了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>在这个世界上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>没有比一胎化政策造成更大损失的决策了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>我们还可以从生理</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>心理和家庭健康的角度讨论一胎化政策</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>现在乳腺癌和子宫癌的发病率很高</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>主要就是由于乳房和子宫很少受到锻炼</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>子女给父母带来极大的满足</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>但独子也给父母带来极大的焦虑</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>这就是为什么国内与小孩有关的机构</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>象学校</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>幼儿园</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>医院</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>留学中介</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>能够收取很高的费用</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>孩子是夫妻关系的纽带</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>孩子多</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>夫妻关系一般会更紧密</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>目前国内的高离婚率</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>是否也是一胎化政策的后果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><span>现在越来越多的人理解到限制生育对中华民族灾难性的后果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>我们该如何解决这个问题呢</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">?</span> <span>很多人把希望寄托在政策的改变上</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>但他们的希望一次次变成失望</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>并非当政者不知限制生育对中华民族造成的灾难</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>但当政者的利益和全民族的利益很少交集</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>任何社会的大变化</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>都是从个人的变化开始</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>从底层的变化开始</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>一个社会的希望</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>在于它的根本</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>在于它的基础</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>也就是说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>在于它的底层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>精英媒体挖苦的超生游击队</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>正是草根阶层顽强维护传统的象征</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>中国目前稍高生育率的社群</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>主要集中在底层</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>耶稣曾经说过</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">, “</span><span>卑微的人得福了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>他们将继承整个世界</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.”</span> <span>因为底层的人能吃苦</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>愿意生孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>世界的未来自然是他们的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>如果很多人都能象他们一样</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>为了多生一个孩子而不顾一切</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>计划生育政策自然就失效了</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>如果有更多反对限制生育的人都不仅仅用语言</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>而且用行动来表达自己的心愿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>我们民族的前途就有了保障</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span><span>我们每个人</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>都是几十亿年进化的结果</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>我们每个人的基因</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>身体和思想</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>都是几十亿年智慧的结晶</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>我们对孩子的喜爱</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,<span> </span></span> <span>对孩子的渴望</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>就是这种智慧最大的体现</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>让我们满足自己的渴望</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>满足自己的心愿</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>早一点生孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>多生几个孩子</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>享受天伦之乐</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>重回春华秋实的生活</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span><span>如果我们自己已过育龄</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>也许可以鼓励下一代早生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>多生</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">.</span> <span>至少</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>我们可以不必给孩子压力</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>让他们追求高学历</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span><span>高收入</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">,</span> <span>而耽误了真正的生活，耽误了生孩子。</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<p><iframe src=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/embeddedform?formkey=dGRpN3FrVThuMFFsZHBZcmNGLW94dEE6MQ\" width=\"450\" height=\"309\" frameborder=\"0\" marginheight=\"0\" marginwidth=\"0\">Loading&#8230;</iframe></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":1004,"categories":[18269,9203],"tags":[9112,9400,9822]}